snippet.title: Blade Ballet - Reveal Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Blade Ballet is a four-player robot deathmatch coming to PS4 in Spring 2016. 

http://bladeballet.com/

Blade Ballet is a whirling dance of multiplayer robot destruction. Each bot possesses a unique personality and special abilities - use them to claim victory as you spin from one challenging arena to the next, battling for dominance. 

http://bladeballet.com/sign-up
